Metallica - 30th Birthday Chopped and Twisted(2CD) 2018 ak320

In 2011 James and the fellas celebrated the 30th anniversary of Metallica.
It was a fuckin awesome party they threw and they did it at the "Home" of 

Metallica no not smog city L.A. But in San Francisco at the Warfield Theater
It was amazing and I have put this Compilation together. Who better than me?
After all I have posted many of my Metallica creations and they have been enjoyed 

by many such as Wired in One Note, Live of Puppets,The revamped and doudled 

Metal Up Your Ass, and of course Time For One Or 3 Or 7. So enough talk.
